Download POES images from http://www.swpc.noaa.gov/

1. Download the index page http://www.swpc.noaa.gov/pmap/Plots.html

2. Look for all the Southern hemisphere plots

3. Check to see if any have not been downloaded

4. If any need to be downloaded, then follow the link to the page with
   the image, then download the GIF image only.
   
5. Once all images have been downloaded, update the composite.

